Year = not significant
========================================================

```{r}
omnr.glm <- data.frame(zone=rep(c("mea","int"),c(16,16)),year=rep(1989:2004,2),suppressed=c(49,10,52,28,5,34,58,33,21,23,12,6,6,11,10,1,137,83,12,79,42,93,199,89,73,150,83,57,101,38,77,16),unsuppressed=c(7,0,14,2,2,4,26,27,6,4,6,0,2,6,6,0,7,5,8,7,1,1,27,54,5,15,12,1,0,10,10,1))
```

```{r}
show(omnr.glm)
```


```{r}
glm.eq0 <- "cbind(suppressed, unsuppressed) ~ year"

glm.eq1 <- "cbind(omnr.glm$suppressed, omnr.glm$unsuppressed) ~ omnr.glm$year"

glm.eq2 <- "cbind(omnr.glm$suppressed, omnr.glm$unsuppressed) ~ omnr.glm$zone * omnr.glm$year"

glm.out <- glm(glm.eq0, family=binomial(logit), data=omnr.glm)
```

```{r}
summary(glm.out)

anova(glm.out, test="Chisq")

```
